{"tid":1165183,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"真民主黨小編，想搵實習既同學仔入一入","createTime":"2019-05-21T15:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T14:07:36.000Z","uid":250449,"like":20,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a7bab85d5dfe3e42618db0bae457422dfd014ee8","tid":1165183,"uid":250449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"廢話唔多講喇，其實是咁的，民主黨請緊實習，最後幾日deadline ，或者你睇新聞對我地有好多意見，但有無諗過有個機會真係將你既諗法帶入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQybkH4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQybkH4.png&h=c34b7175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實習津貼：每小時$40 及約滿津貼$1500<br />\n（無大水喉來講，真係盡左力）<br />\n截止報名日期：5月24日<br />\n面試日期：5月16日起<br />\n實習日期：6月10日至8月2日（150小時）<br />\n<br />\n報名方法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IzVKFB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IzVKFB&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6Tc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=19f33985\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IzVKFB</a><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 可以同胡志偉一齊叫林鄭做八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.P.S 第一次開舖PO，如有違規，請版主手下留情唔好BAN我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a71d0f7599f8217a090ca0e84b1a81a4b6da56","tid":1165183,"uid":109066,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"a7bab85d5dfe3e42618db0bae457422dfd014ee8","tid":1165183,"uid":250449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"廢話唔多講喇，其實是咁的，民主黨請緊實習，最後幾日deadline ，或者你睇新聞對我地有好多意見，但有無諗過有個機會真係將你既諗法帶入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQybkH4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQybkH4.png&h=c34b7175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實習